  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Adventurer! Money is everything, working hard and earning money!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737510/extras/d2beab0d5d236edf5b74918c933176fb.poster.avif?t=1745415159\" width=492 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737510/extras/d2beab0d5d236edf5b74918c933176fb.webm?t=1745415159\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737510/extras/d2beab0d5d236edf5b74918c933176fb.mp4?t=1745415159\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore the map randomly in the lost world.</h2>Random map events waiting to be resolved!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Work hard to make coins, and develop your character. Facing powerful mobs!</h2>Failure is the mother of success. Use gold to upgrade your character.<br>Collect materials to upgrade equipment!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Create buildings to earn more money</h2>Is the income increase too slow?<br>You need more buildings!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Save the villagers and they'll join your team.</h2>Lost villagers are waiting for you to give them a home.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737510/extras/67fdc550cdf136232cb2bebf90a5dfab.poster.avif?t=1745415159\" width=616 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737510/extras/67fdc550cdf136232cb2bebf90a5dfab.webm?t=1745415159\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737510/extras/67fdc550cdf136232cb2bebf90a5dfab.mp4?t=1745415159\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Adventurer! Money is everything, working hard and earning money!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737510/extras/d2beab0d5d236edf5b74918c933176fb.poster.avif?t=1745415159\" width=492 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737510/extras/d2beab0d5d236edf5b74918c933176fb.webm?t=1745415159\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737510/extras/d2beab0d5d236edf5b74918c933176fb.mp4?t=1745415159\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore the map randomly in the lost world.</h2>Random map events waiting to be resolved!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Work hard to make coins, and develop your character. Facing powerful mobs!</h2>Failure is the mother of success. Use gold to upgrade your character.<br>Collect materials to upgrade equipment!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Create buildings to earn more money</h2>Is the income increase too slow?<br>You need more buildings!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Save the villagers and they'll join your team.</h2>Lost villagers are waiting for you to give them a home.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737510/extras/67fdc550cdf136232cb2bebf90a5dfab.poster.avif?t=1745415159\" width=616 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737510/extras/67fdc550cdf136232cb2bebf90a5dfab.webm?t=1745415159\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737510/extras/67fdc550cdf136232cb2bebf90a5dfab.mp4?t=1745415159\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
